e primary series has been completed</td><td><div><p>\"Completed the primary vaccination series\" = TRUE (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Typhoid vaccines\")</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18STyphoidViPSVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Typhoid|20booster|20dose|20was|20administered|20less|20than|203|20years|20ago-225\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Typhoidboosterdosewasadministeredlessthan3yearsago-225\">Typhoid booster dose was administered less than 3 years ago-225</a></td><td>Typhoid booster dose was administered less than 3 years ago</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Typhoid vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Booster dose\") ≥ 1 AND Today's date - Latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Typhoid vaccines\") &lt; 3 years</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
